# Risk Assessment

Potential challenges identified during planning include:

| Risk | Mitigation Strategy |
|------|----------------------|
| Poor dataset quality | Use a verified agricultural dataset |
| Incorrect user input | Validate all input fields |
| Model accuracy issues | Train and evaluate multiple ML algorithms |
| Database errors | Regular testing and backup |
| Deployment issues | Test locally before deployment |

