# Conclusion

The Project Planning Phase established a clear roadmap for developing OptiCrop. By defining the project scope, selecting suitable technologies, identifying milestones, and planning resources, the development process became more structured, efficient, and easier to manage. This planning serves as the foundation for successful implementation and future expansion of the system.